         <abstract><p>
            This set of miracles is part of the Dǝrsāna śǝllāse. The miracles mostly conform to the pattern of
            taʾammǝr, telling of wonders worked by the Trinity both abroad (Egypt, Palestine etc., occasionally
            picking biblical stories) and in Ethiopia.</p>
